yle=\"font-family: var(--font-sans); font-size: 13px; color: var(--sage-text); text-decoration: none;\" data-kid=\"191\">Current Batch</a></li>\n            <li data-kid=\"192\"><a href=\"#\" style=\"font-family: var(--font-sans); font-size: 13px; color: var(--sage-text); text-decoration: none;\" data-kid=\"193\">The Craft</a></li>\n            <li data-kid=\"194\"><a href=\"#\" style=\"font-family: var(--font-sans); font-size: 13px; color: var(--sage-text); text-decoration: none;\" data-kid=\"195\">Inner Circle</a></li>\n            <li data-kid=\"196\"><a href=\"#\" style=\"font-family: var(--font-sans); font-size: 13px; color: var(--sage-text); text-decoration: none; display: flex; align-items: center; gap: 5px;\" data-kid=\"197\">View on Etsy <i data-lucide=\"external-link\" style=\"width: 10px; height: 10px; stroke-width: 1.5;\" data-kid=\"198\"></i></a></li>\n          </ul>\n        </div>\n        \n        <div data-kid=\"199\">\n          <h5 style=\"font-family: var(--font-sans); font-size: 10px; font-weight: 700; text-transform: uppercase; letter-spacing: .25em; color: var(--obsidian); margin: 0 0 20px 0;\" data-kid=\"200\">Assistance</h5>\n          <ul style=\"list-style: none; padding: 0; margin: 0; display: flex; flex-direction: column; gap: 12px;\" data-kid=\"201\">\n            <li data-kid=\"202\"><span style=\"font-family: var(--font-sans); font-size: 13px; color: rgba(95,100,89,0.5);\" data-kid=\"203\">Shipping &amp; Returns</span></li>\n            <li data-kid=\"204\"><span style=\"font-family: var(--font-sans); font-size: 13px; color: rgba(95,100,89,0.5);\" data-kid=\"205\">Wholesale</span></li>\n            <li data-kid=\"206\"><a href=\"#\" style=\"font-family: var(--font-sans); font-size: 13px; color: var(--sage-text); text-decoration: none;\" data-kid=\"207\">Contact</a></li>\n          </ul>\n        </div>\n      </div>\n      \n      <div style=\"border-top: 1px solid rgba(218,203,184,0.4); padding-top: 24px; display: flex; justify-content: space-between; align-items: center;\" data-kid=\"208\">\n        <p style=\"font-family: var(--font-sans); font-size: 11px; color: var(--sage); margin: 0;\" data-kid=\"209\">© 2026 Candera Studio. All rights reserved.</p>\n        <div style=\"display: flex; gap: 24px;\" data-kid=\"210\">\n          <span style=\"font-family: var(--font-sans); font-size: 11px; color: var(--sage); cursor: pointer;\" data-kid=\"211\">Privacy Policy</span>\n          <span style=\"font-family: var(--font-sans); font-size: 11px; color: var(--sage); cursor: pointer;\" data-kid=\"212\">Terms of Service</span>\n        </div>\n      </div>\n    </div>\n  </footer>\n\n</div>\n\n<script data-kid=\"213\">\n  if (window.lucide) lucide.createIcons();\n</script>\n",
