uced. It fills the room without overwhelming the senses — and the vessel becomes a relic long after the burn.\"</p>\n      <div style=\"display:flex;align-items:center;justify-content:center;gap:12px;\" data-kid=\"118\">\n        <div style=\"width:32px;height:1px;background:#dacbb8;\" data-kid=\"119\"></div>\n        <p style=\"font-family:'DM Sans',sans-serif;font-size:12px;font-weight:300;color:#5f6459;margin:0;\" data-kid=\"120\">Elena Marroquín, Los Angeles</p>\n        <div style=\"width:32px;height:1px;background:#dacbb8;\" data-kid=\"121\"></div>\n      </div>\n    </div>\n    \n    <div style=\"border-top:1px solid rgba(218,204,184,0.5);border-bottom:1px solid rgba(218,204,184,0.5);padding:24px 0;display:flex;justify-content:center;gap:64px;align-items:center;\" data-kid=\"122\">\n      <div style=\"text-align:center;\" data-kid=\"123\">\n        <p style=\"font-family:'DM Sans',sans-serif;font-size:13px;font-weight:300;color:#141412;margin:0 0 4px 0;\" data-kid=\"124\">Will Thorne</p>\n        <span style=\"font-family:'DM Sans',sans-serif;font-size:9px;font-weight:600;text-transform:uppercase;letter-spacing:0.18em;color:#7a8174;\" data-kid=\"125\">Repeat Collector · Austin</span>\n      </div>\n      <div style=\"width:1px;height:32px;background:rgba(218,204,184,0.5);\" data-kid=\"126\"></div>\n      <div style=\"text-align:center;\" data-kid=\"127\">\n        <p style=\"font-family:'DM Sans',sans-serif;font-size:13px;font-weight:300;color:#141412;margin:0 0 4px 0;\" data-kid=\"128\">Sasha B.</p>\n        <span style=\"font-family:'DM Sans',sans-serif;font-size:9px;font-weight:600;text-transform:uppercase;letter-spacing:0.18em;color:#7a8174;\" data-kid=\"129\">Verified Ritualist · Brooklyn</span>\n      </div>\n      <div style=\"width:1px;height:32px;background:rgba(218,204,184,0.5);\" data-kid=\"130\"></div>\n      <div style=\"text-align:center;\" data-kid=\"131\">\n        <p style=\"font-family:'DM Sans',sans-serif;font-size:13px;font-weight:300;color:#141412;margin:0 0 4px 0;\" data-kid=\"132\">Elena Marroquín</p>\n        <span style=\"font-family:'DM Sans',sans-serif;font-size:9px;font-weight:600;text-transform:uppercase;letter-spacing:0.18em;color:#7a8174;\" data-kid=\"133\">Verified Ritualist · Los Angeles</span>\n      </div>\n    </div>\n  </div>\n</div>\n\n\n<div style=\"background:#141412;display:grid;grid-template-columns:1fr 1fr;\" data-kid=\"134\">\n  <div style=\"position:relative;overflow:hidden;min-height:560px;\" data-kid=\"135\">\n    <img src=\"/api/local/images/Candera Design System/assets/images/crimson-noir.jpg\" alt=\"Crimson Noir candle\" decoding=\"async\" loading=\"lazy\" style=\"width:100%;height:100%;object-fit:cover;display:block;object-position:center;\" data-kid=\"136\">\n    <div style=\"position:absolute;inset:0;background:linear-gradient(to right,transparent 60%,rgba(20,20,18,0.5) 100%);\" data-kid=\"137\"></div>\n  </div>\n  <div style=\"display:flex;flex-direction:column;justify-content:center;padding:80px 80px 80px 72px;\" data-kid=\"138\">\n    <p style=\"font-family:'DM Sans',sans-serif;font-size:10px;font-weight:700;text-transform:uppercase;letter-spacing:0.3em;color:#b28c9c;margin:0 0 16px 0;\" data-kid=\"139\">The Inner Circle</p>\n    <h2 style=\"font-family:'Fraunces',Georgia,serif;font-style:italic;font-weight:400;font-size:40px;line-height:1.15;letter-spacing:-0.01em;color:#f0ebe3;margin:0 0 20px 0;font-optical-sizing:auto;\" data-kid=\"140\">Join the Inner Circle.</h2>\n    <p style=\"font-family:'DM Sans',sans-serif;font-size:15px;font-weight:300;color:rgba(240,235,227,0.62);line-height:1.75;margin:0 0 40px 0;max-width:360px;\" data-kid=\"141\">Our batches sell out in days. Join our list to receive early access to new scent drops and personal ritual invitations.</p>\n    <div style=\"display:flex;border-bottom:1px solid rgba(255,255,255,0.22);margin-bottom:14px;max-width:400px;\" data-kid=\"142\">\n      <input type=\"email\" aria-label=\"Email address for Inner Circle\" placeholder=\"Your email address\" style=\"flex:1;background:transparent;border:none;outline:none;font-family:'DM Sans',sans-serif;font-size:13px;font-weight:300;color:#f0ebe3;padding:12px 0;caret-color:#b28c9c;\" data-kid=\"143\">\n      <button class=\"ic-btn\" data-kid=\"144\">Request Entry</button>\n    </div>\n    <p style=\"font-family:'EB Garamond',Georgia,serif;font-style:italic;font-size:13px;color:rgba(240,235,227,0.32);margin:0;\" data-kid=\"145\">This is not a newsletter. It is a correspondence.</p>\n  </div>\n</div>\n\n\n<footer style=\"background:#fdfbf7;padding:80px 0 48px 0;border-top:1px solid rgba(218,204,184,0.45);position:relative;overflow:hidden;\" data-kid=\"146\">\n  <div aria-hidden=\"true\" style=\"position:absolute;bottom:-24px;right:-8px;font-family:'Fraunces',Georgia,serif;font-weight:700;font-size:180px;letter-spacing:-0.04em;color:rgba(20,20,18,0.038);line-height:1;pointer-events:none;user-select:none;\" data-kid=\"147\">CANDERA</div>\n  <div style=\"max-width:1280px;margin:0 auto;padding:0 40px;position:relative;z-index:1;\" data-kid=\"148\">\n    <div style=\"display:grid;grid-template-columns:2fr 1fr 1fr;gap:64px;\" data-kid=\"149\">\n      <div data-kid=\"150\">\n        <a href=\"#\" style=\"font-family:'Fraunces',Georgia,serif;font-weight:700;font-size:20px;letter-spacing:-0.02em;color:#141412;text-decoration:none;display:block;margin-bottom:12px;\" data-kid=\"151\">CANDERA</a>\n        <p style=\"font-family:'EB Garamond',Georgia,serif;font-style:italic;font-size:13px;color:#7a8174;line-height:1.7;margin:0 0 24px 0;max-width:280px;\" data-kid=\"152\">Cultivating intentional living through scent and micro-batch artisanry. Based in the studio, shared everywhere.</p>\n        <div style=\"display:flex;gap:16px;\" data-kid=\"153\">\n          <a href=\"#\" style=\"color:#7a8174;display:inline-flex;transition:color 150ms;\" onmouseover=\"this.style.color='#dd7d52'\" onmouseout=\"this.style.color='#7a8174'\" data-kid=\"154\"><i 